<L><HI>Commanding</HI> Pow'r reign'd in her <HI>&s;parkling</HI> Eye,</L>
<L>And on her <HI>Brow</HI> &s;ate <HI>awful</HI> Maje&s;ty.</L>
<L>A &s;prightly <HI>Vigour</HI> fill'd her Manly Face,</L>
