<LG>
<L>THo' the &s;harp &s;entence, which, in too great ha&s;t,<NOTE PLACE="marg">2 <HI>Sam.</HI> 13.</NOTE></L>
<L>Th' unwitting King upon him&s;elf had plac'd,</L>
<L>$as mitigated, by the Clemency</L>
<L><HI>David</HI>'s God; that <HI>David</HI> might not Dy:</L>
