<L>Was <HI>Tamar</HI>; a mo&s;t beautiful young Dame.</L>
<L>Si&s;ter &s;he was to <HI>Ab&s;alom</HI> the Fair,</L>
<L><HI>David</HI>'s Third Son; &s;o noted for his Hair.</L>
<L><PB N="185" REF="201">On this Half-Si&s;ter-Princes, <HI>Amnon</HI> ca&s;t</L>
<L>$word$ wanton Eye. Affection grew &s;o fa&s;t</L>
<L>$pon him, that, not daring to di&s;cover,</L>
