<L>$e was; He <HI>Pin'd</HI> away, his <HI>Cheeks</HI> grew <HI>pale</HI>,</L>
<L>$s <HI>Fle&s;h</HI> did <HI>wa&s;t</HI>, His <HI>Strength</HI> began to <HI>fail</HI>.</L>
<L>$he <HI>fi'ery Pa&s;&s;ion</HI>, in his Bo&s;om pent,</L>
