<DIV2 N="4" TYPE="chapter">
<HEAD>CHAP. IV.</HEAD>
<LG>
<L>$word$ The <HI>Intemp'rance</HI> of th' <HI>ambitious</HI> Mind!<NOTE PLACE="marg">2 <HI>Sam.</HI> 15.</NOTE></L>
