<L>$word$ not yet &s;ilenc'd: but <HI>&s;till Cry's aloud</HI>.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<PB N="218" REF="234">
<L>To <HI>Hebron</HI> now Prince <HI>Ab&s;alom</HI> doth Po&s;t,</L>
